  "title": "Endoscopy Nurse (Office Hours / Central / Private Clinic)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Profile</strong></p>\n<p>Founded over 20 years ago, we are a leading healthcare group in Singapore offering a wide range of diagnostic, imaging, and advanced treatment services. Our network includes specialist clinics, modern imaging centres, and facilities providing cutting-edge cancer therapies. We focus on early detection, precision diagnostics, and personalised care to support better patient outcomes. As an organisation, we are committed to clinical excellence, innovation, and a seamless patient experience.</p>\n<p><strong>Work location: Orchard</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Working hours: 5.5 days work week (Mon – Fri and half Sat)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assess and admit patients for endoscopy procedures (i.e., gastroscopy, colonoscopy, ERCP etc.)</li>\n  <li>Prepare and set up endoscopes and required equipment.</li>\n  <li>Assist the endoscopist during procedures and monitor patient safety, including those under sedation.</li>\n  <li>Clean, disinfect, and reprocess endoscopes, procedure rooms and other equipment according to infection-control standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Key Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min. Diploma in Nursing or Specialist Diploma in Endoscopy Nursing with SNB registration</li>\n  <li>Min. 1-2 years’ experience in nursing duties (preferably in endoscopy suite or day surgery environment)</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of endoscopy procedures, techniques, and common complications.</li>\n  <li>Able to speak in Mandarin Chinese to liaise with Chinese-speaking patients on a daily basis</li>\n</ul>\n<p>📩 Your recruiter: <strong>WhatsApp your CV/resume to Celine</strong> at <strong>8977 7051 </strong>for a quicker response.</p>\n<p>You may also drop your resume via email to celinechan@envirodynamics.com.sg – only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Celine Chan I Reg. No: R21103433</p>\n<p>EnviroDynamics Solutions Pte Ltd I EA License No.: 12C6285</p>",
